items.label: Cascade
items.detail: Delete the child records when the parent record is deleted.

items.label: Restrict
items.detail: Prevent deleting a parent record as long as it is referenced.

items.label: NoAction
items.detail: Prevent deleting a parent record as long as it is referenced.

items.label: SetNull
items.detail: Set the referencing fields to NULL when the referenced record is deleted.

items.label: SetDefault
items.detail: Set the referencing field's value to the default when the referenced record is deleted.
